Carol Wayne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carol_Wayne 0 Carol Wayne (September 6, 1942 – January 13, 1985) was an American television and film actress. She made numerous appearances on The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson as the Matinee Lady in the Art Fern's Tea Time Movie sketches.
